    <section id="newsletter" class="px-4 py-5 bg-accent">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <form class="col-lg-7">
                    <h2 class="text-dark">
                        Kickstart Your Path to Wellness Today—No Program Sign-Up
                        Required!
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        Unlock a healthier, more active life with our free
                        newsletter. Discover simple yet effective exercise tips,
                        delicious plant-based recipes, and gain exclusive access
                        to insightful workshops and special offers. It's your
                        chance to take meaningful steps towards wellness, guided
                        by Cindy's expertise, without committing to a program.
                        Dive in now for free resources that empower your journey
                        to well-being. Sign up and let's embark on this
                        transformative adventure together.
                    </p>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row w-100 gap-2">
                        <label for="newsletter1" class="visually-hidden"
